text:
As we celebrate the release of Kai Li, I have renewed hope and urgency for other hostages and political prisoners abroad.

@POTUS, thank you for this incredible breakthrough. There is still time to build on these accomplishments. 

Please see my letter to President Biden urging him to use the remaining months of his presidency to bring home the American hostages still held by Hamas, including my constituent Omer Neutra, and Uyghur political prisoner Gulshan Abbas, still imprisoned in China.
